Installing pyfits & friends:

Preliminary packages:

> sudo apt-get install python-pip python-dev python-scipy git

This installs python's own package management system

Now you can use pip to install python packages:

> sudo pip install numpy pyfits xlrd

- Command Line Usage:

> ./fitsproc.py <input> <ku|l> <sigma>

- Installation

To install the entire system (ideal for fresh system):
> sudo make dist-install

To only install the CGI scripts (less destructive)
> sudo make dist-install
